{"tid":309520,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"近排好似諸事不順咁，係咪奶咗野？","createTime":"2017-07-05T05:47:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-06T15:48:45.000Z","uid":89924,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"10a84109a6eb96d073981ac60570687110a2e314","tid":309520,"uid":89924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T05:47:31.000Z","msg":"朝早返工做野double check咗幾次都錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n放工返學遇著班完全唔識做野既groupmate<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n放學返到屋企連部電腦都玩鳩我開唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n早兩日仲比我見到我個移咗民既fd返黎香港竟然唔通知我同我食餐飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n朋友堆入面畢業出黎做野際遇最差就係我，而我而家又係朋友堆入面唯一一個仲係一支公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢段時間最令我感到安慰既可能係放學返屋企果時無人同我同lift等我可以係部lift到鳩叫下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"589733b5bacb31991f4d5f11c411f80ecce14658","tid":309520,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T06:00:52.000Z","msg":"性交轉運"},{"pid":"dd5ce62c4bda06a6097e469104b4c8df0f8dd4cf","tid":309520,"uid":88190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T08:26:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>朝早返工做野double check咗幾次都錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n放工返學遇著班完全唔識做野既groupmate<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n放學返到屋企連部電腦都玩鳩我開唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n早兩日仲比我見到我個移咗民既fd返黎香港竟然唔通知我同我食餐飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n朋友堆入面畢業出黎做野際遇最差就係我，而我而家又係朋友堆入面唯一一個仲係一支公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢段時間最令我感到安慰既可能係放學返屋企果時無人同我同lift等我可以係部lift到鳩叫下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n樓主你番工又番學，都好大壓力，會唔會需要時間休息下??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88a21032d464b95eeb226b8b879290e39f3e2fb2","tid":309520,"uid":1510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T08:27:11.000Z","msg":"我都係 好似好黑"},{"pid":"4a43be7bc4fcbcb3dddde4f214581d4e583c9d94","tid":309520,"uid":6869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T08:35:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"35e80b6c543828a857b41ffa76228d9f1789b83d","tid":309520,"uid":89924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T09:25:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無打j先<br />\n打j會令人黑仔</blockquote><br />\n打j剩係會黑條j<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a0a2b6da19ee7be8b31b243725ddf4a1c8b9f1b","tid":309520,"uid":89924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T09:33:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>朝早返工做野double check咗幾次都錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n放工返學遇著班完全唔識做野既groupmate<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n放學返到屋企連部電腦都玩鳩我開唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n早兩日仲比我見到我個移咗民既fd返黎香港竟然唔通知我同我食餐飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n朋友堆入面畢業出黎做野際遇最差就係我，而我而家又係朋友堆入面唯一一個仲係一支公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢段時間最令我感到安慰既可能係放學返屋企果時無人同我同lift等我可以係部lift到鳩叫下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n樓主你番工又番學，都好大壓力，會唔會需要時間休息下??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不了我仲要繼續搏殺<br />\n<br />\n怪就怪細細個讀書唔錯，身邊d同學大部分都係專業人士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 次次聚會都好大壓力<br />\n<br />\n有次比班fd問我幾錢人工,佢打死都唔信我真係搵得果萬一蚊都唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 果下真係好有挫敗感<br />\n<br />\n有時我真係唔怕辛苦，但真係希望辛苦完係有回報,哪怕係少少既回報都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔洗搵幾萬蚊一個月，只係搵到份同讀緊既書有關係既工,幾千蚊都好，比我儲下經驗已經好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最怕係讀完同無讀一樣，最後都係做返普通白領，咁就真係尬好灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f55611493ebab1a6fd79aff2f82bb382a66c75e","tid":309520,"uid":89924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:21:41.000Z","msg":"尋既做project見到個groupmate交出黎份野得正常長度既五分一已經好灰<br />\n<br />\n今日仲要係公司收錯錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 返工返到要貼錢返工真係好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然係幾十蚊但係都夠我食餐飯了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2b8a280fd408abc9845e608f371d06676abd9b3","tid":309520,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:23:20.000Z","msg":"仲未接受到自己係一條柴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n接受左之後生活會輕鬆d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6131d82cf9d1f5886d340fed5de9801974ff5576","tid":309520,"uid":89924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:47:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲未接受到自己係一條柴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n接受左之後生活會輕鬆d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n搵食都難，仲點輕鬆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3c87185d1b1dbf103b9e71fb0ad19c01389e354","tid":309520,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T15:48:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}